description: Triangle, read by rows, where T(n,k) equals the dot product of the vector of terms in row n-1 from T(n-1,k) to T(n-1,n-1) with the vector of terms in column k+1 from T(k+1,k+1) to T(n,k+1): T(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..n-k-1} T(n-1,j+k)*T(j+k+1,k+1) for n>k+1>0, with T(n,n) = 1 and T(n,n-1) = n (n>=1).
